title: Ornette Coleman - Languages (live in 1968) Moon
description:
ORNETTE COLEMAN - LANGUAGES

1. Tutti [22:59]
2. Three Wise Men And The Saint [13:45]
3. New York [18:48]

Ornette Coleman - alto sax
Charlie Haden - bass
David Izenzon- bass
Ed Blackwell - drums

Recorded live in Milano, February 5, 1968

1993 Moon Records

This is a great concert, but be warned, it doesn't sound like a professional quality recording.



RIP Ornette Coleman (March 9, 1930 - June 11, 2015)
